# 6. Anti-Patterns (DO NOT DO)

## MUST NOT

- begin work without reading governance docs
- assume prior context is sufficient for new tasks
- ignore precedence chain when conflicts arise
- treat constraints as optional guidelines
- commit without running `make preflight`

---

# 7. Validation Checklist

Before starting any work:

- [ ] `CONTEXT.md` read
- [ ] `AGENTS.md` read
- [ ] all mandatory docs read
- [ ] precedence chain understood
- [ ] non-negotiable constraints acknowledged
- [ ] `make preflight` will be run before committing
